## Shipments [/shipments{?orderId}]

### Get order shipments [GET]
Returns all shipments for specific orderId. Each record contains only one type of item. Data from this endpoint are for Amazon fulfilled orders (FBA) only and are updated once a day due to Amazon's speed of updating.

(NOTE: Amazon made changes to their API and we are no longer able to obtain the following: billAddress, billCity, billState, billPostalCode, billCountry)

+ Parameters
    + orderId - string

+ Request

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer <token>


+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes ( array[ Shipment ] )

## Order Financial Events [/finances/orderevents{?fromPostedDate}]

### Get order financial events [GET]
Returns up to 100 events by posted date.
You can paginate naturally through events by taking `postedDate` attribute of the last event on a page and making the request again with this new value in your query.

+ Parameters
    + fromPostedDate - string - ISO date

+ Request

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer <token>


+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes ( array[ OrderFinancialEvent ] )

## Returns [/returns{?fromReturnDate}]

### Get order returns [GET]
Returns up to 100 records by return date.

Data from this endpoint are for Amazon fulfilled orders (FBA) only and are updated once a day.

+ Parameters
    + fromReturnDate - string - ISO date

+ Request

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer <token>


+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes ( array[ Return ] )

## Return Labels [/return-labels{?marketplace}{?marketplaceOrderId}]

### Create a return label request [POST]
Creates a return label request.

> **NOTE**: It is necessary to have a return address setup first. You must contact support.

+ Parameters
    + marketplace - string
    + marketplaceOrderId - string

+ Request

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer <token>

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes ( ReturnLabel )

### Get return label requests for order [GET]

+ Parameters
    + marketplace - string
    + marketplaceOrderId - string

+ Request

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer <token>

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes ( array[ ReturnLabel ] )

# Data Structures

## Order (object)

+ marketplace ( MarketplaceName )
+ marketplaceOrderId: `xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx` ( string )
+ lastChanged: `2019-01-01T00:00:00.000Z` ( string ) - ISO date
+ buyer ( Buyer )
+ delivery ( OrderDelivery, optional )
+ currencyCode: EUR ( string )
+ items ( array[ OrderItem ] )
+ fulfillmentChannel ( MarketplaceFulfillment )
+ status ( Status )
+ shippingPrice: 3.99 ( number ) - **Deprecated!** Use `price.delivery.[withTax|withoutTax]`
+ totalItemTax: 21.26 ( number ) - **Deprecated!** Use `price.items.tax`
+ totalDiscount: 3.99 ( number ) - **Deprecated!** Use `price.totalDiscount.[withTax|withoutTax]`
+ totalPrice: 121.89 ( number ) - **Deprecated!** Use `price.total.[withTax|withoutTax]`
+ price ( OrderPrice, required ) - Breakdown of order price.
+ payment ( Payment, required )
+ purchaseDate: `2019-01-01T00:00:00.000Z` ( string ) - ISO date
+ pendingDate: `2019-01-01T00:00:00.000Z` ( string ) - ISO date
+ unshippedDate: `2019-01-01T00:00:00.000Z` ( string ) - ISO date
+ shippedDate: `2019-01-01T00:00:00.000Z` ( string ) - ISO date
+ canceledDate: `2019-01-01T00:00:00.000Z` ( string ) - ISO date
+ latestShipDate: `2019-01-01T00:00:00.000Z` ( string ) - ISO date
+ latestDeliveryDate: `2019-01-01T00:00:00.000Z` ( string ) - ISO date
+ shipServiceLevel: Expedited ( string )
+ deliveryBranchId ( number )
+ invoices ( array[ Invoice ] )
+ isBusinessOrder: false ( boolean )
+ isPremiumOrder: false ( boolean )
+ isPrime: false ( boolean )
+ isComplete: true ( boolean ) - If order has gathered all the information from marketplace.
+ isRefunded: false ( boolean )
+ paymentMethod ( PaymentMethod ) - **Deprecated!** Use `payment.paymentMethod` instead
+ invoiceUrls ( array[ string ] ) - **Deprecated!** Use `invoices` instead.
+ cashOnDelivery ( CashOnDelivery ) - **Deprecated!** Use `payment.cashOnDelivery` instead.
+ cancelRequest ( CancelRequest, optional )
+ returnLabels ( array[ OrderReturnLabel ], optional )

## OrderPrice (object)
+ items ( Price ) - Total price for order line items
+ delivery ( Price ) - Price of delivery
+ payment ( Price ) - Price of applied payment method (e.g. cash on delivery service fee)
+ totalDiscount ( Price ) - Total discount **applied** to order (amount is already subtracted from order total)
+ total ( Price, required ) - Order total price.

## Price (object)
+ withTax: 1200 ( number, optional ) - Price value incl. tax (is required if `withoutTax` is undefined)
+ withoutTax: 1000 ( number, optional ) - Price value excluding tax (is required if `withTax` is undefined)
+ tax: 200 ( number, optional ) - Value of applied tax
+ taxRatePercent: 20 ( number, optional ) - **Deprecated!** Use `taxRatePercentDecimal` instead - Integer tax rate in %
+ taxRatePercentDecimal: 20 ( number, optional ) - Decimal tax rate in %

## OrderItem (object)

+ sku: abc ( string ) - your ID of the product
+ asin: B005JID0ER ( string ) - amazon ID of the product
+ marketplaceItemId: 00000000000000 ( string )
+ name: example ( string )
+ price: 117.9 ( number ) - price of items with tax without shipping price
+ itemPrice: 58.95 ( number ) - price of one item (price divided by quantity)
+ quantity: 2 ( number )
+ tax: 21.26 ( number ) - tax for items (absolute number)
+ promotionDiscount: 0 ( number ) - **Deprecated!** Use `lineItemDiscount.[withTax|withoutTax]`
+ promotionDiscountTax: 0 ( number )  - **Deprecated!** Use `lineItemDiscount.tax`
+ shippingDiscount: 0 ( number )  - **Deprecated!** Use `deliveryDiscount.[withTax|withoutTax]`
+ shippingDiscountTax: 0 ( number ) - **Deprecated!** Use `deliveryDiscount.tax`
+ shippingPrice: 3.99 ( number )  - **Deprecated!** Use `deliveryPrice.[withTax|withoutTax]`
+ shippingTax: 0.72 ( number )  - **Deprecated!** Use `deliveryPrice.tax`
+ lineItemPrice ( Price, required ) - Price of the order line item (applied quantity).
+ lineItemDiscount ( Price ) - Applied discount for line item price.
+ deliveryPrice ( Price ) - Price for delivery of the line item (applied quantity).
+ deliveryDiscount ( Price ) - Applied discount for line item delivery price.
+ marketplaceCommission ( Price ) - Marketplace's commission on the ordered item.
+ buyerCustomInfo ( array[ BuyerCustomInfo ] )

## Buyer (object)

+ name: `name surname` ( string)
+ email: example@example.com ( string )
+ addressLine ( array[ string ] ) - max 3 items
+ city: city ( string )
+ countryCode: AA ( string )
+ country: country ( string )
+ district: district ( string )
+ phone: 00000000000 ( string )
+ zipCode: 00000000 ( string )
+ stateOrRegion: `state/region` ( string )
+ taxId: XX000000000 ( string )
+ taxCountry: AA ( string )

## OrderDelivery (object)

+ shippingCarrier: `Czech Post` ( string, optional )
+ shippingCarrierService: `Do ruky` ( string, optional )

## Payment (object)

+ paymentMethod ( OrderPaymentMethod, required )
+ cashOnDelivery ( PaymentCashOnDelivery, optional )

## PaymentCashOnDelivery (object)
+ toPay (number, optional)
+ servicePrice (number, optional)

