## MarketplaceFulfillment (enum)
- Seller
- MediatedCarrier
- FBA

## Status (enum)
- Unshipped
- Pending
- Shipped
- Canceled

## PaymentMethod (enum)
- Other
- COD
- CVSs

## OrderPaymentMethod (enum)
- CreditCard
- CashOnDelivery

## BuyerCustomInfo (object)
+ name: `CustomizedURL` ( string )
+ value: `https://zme-caps.amazon.com/t/xxxxxxxxxxxx/XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX/00` ( string )

## PackageItem (object)
+ marketplaceItemId: `ID12340` (string, required) - Alza: item identifier | Amazon: orderItemId
+ quantity: `2` (number, required) - minimal value 0

## package (object)
+ number: `PK001` (string, required) - Alza: package identifier | Amazon: packageReferenceId seller-supplied identifier
+ weight: `2.5` (number, required) - Alza: Minimal value 0.1 | Amazon: Not used
+ fullNumber: `12345` (string, nullable) - Alza: trackingNumber | Amazon: trackingNumber
+ items: (array[PackageItem], required) - Items included in package

## InputFulfillment
+ marketplaceOrderId: `xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx` ( string, required )
+ marketplace ( MarketplaceName, required )
+ status ( FulfillmentStatus, required )
+ trackingNumber: 0000000000 ( string, nullable ) - **required for Mall & Alza**, for all statuses
+ fullNumber: 000000000000 ( string, nullable ) - **optional for Alza**, only applied if weight is provided
+ trackingUrl: `https://your-carrier.com/track/0000000000` ( string, nullable ) - **required for Mall**
+ carrier ( CarrierCode )
+ carrierName ( string, nullable )
+ shipDate: `2019-01-01T00:00:00.000Z` ( string, nullable ) - ISO date
+ weight: `5` (number) - **required for Alza** in `Shipped` status
+ cashOnDeliveryValue: `890` (number) - **required for Alza** in `Shipped` status
+ cashOnDeliveryCurrency: `CZK` (string) - **required for Alza** in `Shipped` status
+ shipmentValue: `890` (number) - **required for Alza** in `Shipped` status
+ shipmentValueCurrency: `CZK` (string) - **required for Alza** in `Shipped` status
+ parcelShop (ParcelShop) - **optional for Alza** in `Shipped` status
+ parcelShopBranchCode (string) - **optional for Alza** in `Shipped` status
+ cancelReason (CancelReason) - **optional for Amazon** in `Canceled` status
+ shipMethod: `DHL Express` ( string, optional ) - **optional for Amazon**
+ packages (array[package], optional) - **optional for Alza & Amazon** List of packages included in the fulfillment


## CashOnDelivery
+ value: 0 ( number )
+ currency: EUR ( string )
+ variableSymbol ( string )

## CancelRequest
+ cancelReason: BuyerCanceled ( CancelReason )
+ marketplaceCancelReason ( string )

## OrderReturnLabel
+ status ( OrderReturnLabelStatus, required )
+ requestCreatedAt ( string, required )
+ shipmentNumber ( string, required )
+ labelNumber ( number, required )
+ packageLabelUrls ( array[ string ], required )
+ errorMessage ( string, optional )


## Invoice
+ id: `INV-FR-000000000-2019-00` ( string )
+ type: `SHIPMENT` ( string ) - Expected values are SHIPMENT and REFUND
+ url: `https://www.Amazon.fr/gp/invoice/download.html?v=urn%3aalx%3aver%3a01dcc42c-0000-000a-aaa0-00000a000aa0&t=EU_Retail_Forward` ( string )
+ date: `2019-01-01T00:00:00.000Z` ( string ) - ISO date

## Fulfillment
+ marketplaceOrderId: `xxx-xxxxxxx-xxxxxxx` ( string, required )
+ marketplaceOrderIds: `xxx-xxxxxxx-xxxxxxx` ( array [string], required )
+ marketplace ( MarketplaceName, required )
+ status ( FulfillmentStatus, required )
+ trackingNumber: 0000000000 ( string, optional )
+ trackingUrl: `https://your-carrier.com/track/0000000000` ( string, optional )
+ carrier ( CarrierCode )
+ carrierName ( string, optional )
+ shipDate: `2019-01-01T00:00:00.000Z` ( string, nullable ) - ISO date
+ lastChanged: `2019-01-01T00:00:00.000Z` ( string ) - ISO date
+ shipMethod: `DHL Express` ( string, optional )

## FulfillmentStatus ( enum )
- Registered
- Shipped
- AtDepot
- OutForDelivery
- Delivered
- Failed
- Canceled


