## Shipment (object)
- marketplace: amazon_de (string) - can be empty
- marketplaceOrderId: `xxx-xxxxxxx-xxxxxxx` (string)
- shipmentId: DckjR9T7L (string)
- shipmentItemId: DYr1tCWKR (string)
- sku (string)
- quantity (number)
- sellerCentralId: MUC3 (string)
- carrier (string)
- trackingNumber: AA0000000000 (string)
- billAddress (string) - can be empty - see NOTE
- billCity (string) - can be empty - see NOTE
- billState (string) - can be empty - see NOTE
- billPostalCode (string) - can be empty - see NOTE
- billCountry (string) - can be empty - see NOTE
- currency: EUR (string)
- itemPromotionDiscount: 0 (number)
- shipPromotionDiscount: `-1.2` (number)
- shipmentDate: `2019-01-01T00:00:00.000Z` ( string ) - ISO date
- estimatedArrivalDate: `2019-01-03T00:00:00.000Z` ( string ) - ISO date

## AmountItem (object)
- name ( string )
- amount ( number )

## AdditionalFinancialItem (object)
- type: `TaxWithheld` ( string )
- taxCollectionModel: `MarketplaceFacilitator`  ( string )
- chargeType: `MarketplaceFacilitatorVAT-Principal` ( string )
- amount: 12.34 ( number )

## OrderFinancialEventItem (object)
- itemId: 00000000000000 ( string )
- quantity ( number )
- sku ( string )
- name ( string )
- charges ( array[AmountItem] )
- fees ( array[AmountItem] )
- additionalItems ( array[AdditionalFinancialItem] )
- costOfPointsGranted ( number )
- costOfPointsReturned ( number )
- withheldTax ( number )
- promotions ( number )
- currency: EUR ( string )

## OrderFinancialEventType (enum)
- Payment
- Refund
- Chargeback

## OrderFinancialEvent (object)
- marketplaceOrderId: `xxx-xxxxxxx-xxxxxxx` ( string )
- marketplace: amazon_de ( MarketplaceName )
- postedDate: `2019-01-01T00:00:00.000Z` ( string ) - ISO date
- type ( OrderFinancialEventType )
- items ( array[OrderFinancialEventItem] )

## Return (object)
- returnDate: `2019-01-01T00:00:00.000Z` ( string ) - ISO date
- marketplaceOrderId: `xxx-xxxxxxx-xxxxxxx` ( string )
- sku ( string )
- asin ( string )
- fnSku ( string )
- productName ( string )
- quantity ( number )
- fulfillmentCenterId ( string )
- detailedDisposition ( string )
- reason ( string )
- status ( string )
- licensePlateNumber ( string )
- customerComments ( string )

## PackageLabelData
+ status ( ResourceStatuses ) 
+ packageLabels: https://url.to/pdf?abcasdasdasd ( string, optional )
+ packageLabelsId: `abc-123-456` ( string )
+ packages ( array[ FulfillmentPackage ] )
+ failReason: Maximum number of required packages exceeded. Actual limit is 1.  ( string )

## LabelMarketplace (enum)
- alza_cz

## CreateLabelInput
+ marketplaceOrderIds: `abc-123-456`, `efg-456-789` ( array[string], required )
+ packages ( array[PackageInput], optional )


## PackageInput
+ weight: 3 ( number, required )
+ items ( array[PackageInputItem] )

## PackageInputItem
+ marketplaceOrderId: `moi-123-xxx` ( string, required )
+ marketplaceItemId: `mid-123-zzz` ( string, required )
+ quantity: 1 ( number, required )

## ResourceStatuses (enum)
- Generated
- Generating
- Failed

## CancelReason (enum)
+ NoInventory
+ ShippingAddressUndeliverable
+ CustomerExchange
+ BuyerCanceled
+ GeneralAdjustment
+ CarrierCreditDecision
+ RiskAssessmentInformationNotValid
+ CarrierCoverageFailure
+ CustomerReturn
+ MerchandiseNotReceived
+ CannotVerifyInformation
+ PricingError
+ RejectOrder
+ WeatherDelay

## OrderReturnLabelStatus (enum)
+ Pending
+ Creating
+ Created
+ Error

## FulfillmentPackageItem
+ marketplaceItemId: `123-1bc-222` ( string )
+ marketplaceOrderId: `abc-efg-145` ( string )
+ quantity ( number )


## FulfillmentPackage
+ weight: 3 ( number )
+ items ( array[FulfillmentPackageItem] )

## ShippingList
+ shippingListId: 123-abcd-456 ( string, required )
+ pdf: www.example.com ( string, required )

## AlzaShipment
+ departureTime: `2019-01-01T00:00:00.000Z` ( string, optional ) - ISO date
+ shippingList ( ShippingList, required )

## BranchBarcodesBatchInput
+ marketplaceOrderIds: 4252154192, 4251962062 ( array[string], required )
+ operation: `BarcodeBatch` (enum[string], optional ) - Operation what will be used to generate document
    + Members
        + `BarcodeBatch`
        + `BarcodeWithEanBatch`

## BranchBarcodesBatch
+ pdfId: `5f64578e2feb3dc8f4703749` ( string, required ) - Unique ID of the generated PDF document
+ pdfDocumentType: `BarcodeBatch` (enum[string], required ) - Operation used to generate document
    + Members
        + `BarcodeBatch`
        + `BarcodeWithEanBatch`
+ downloadUrl: https://download.link.com/for/document.pdf ( string, required ) - Download URL of the generated PDF document
+ barcodes: BCX846680925,BCX846442464 ( array[ string ], required ) - Barcodes that are present in the generated PDF document (can contain duplicates)

## PickupLists 
 + carrier: DHL ( CarrierCode, required ) - Shipping carrier
 + carrierPickupListId: 123456 ( number, required ) - Carrier's identification of the pickup list
 + pickupTime: `2020-12-30T00:00:00.000Z` ( string, required ) - Expected time of pickup by the carrier, in UTC
 + downloadUrl: `https://download.link.com/for/document.pdf` ( string, required ) - Download URL of the pickup list in PDF
 + marketplaceOrderIds: `abc-123-456`, `efg-456-789` ( array[string], required ) - `marketplaceOrderId`s of orders included on this pickup list
 + lastChanged: `2020-12-30T00:00:00.000Z` ( string, required ) - Time of the last change made to the pickup list, in UTC

## ReturnLabel
+ marketplace: amazon_de ( string, required )
+ marketplaceOrderId: 123-1234567-123 ( string, required )
+ state: Resolved ( ReturnLabelState, required )
+ referenceId: return-amazon-de-123-1234567-123 ( string, required )
+ note: Company XYZ ( string, optional )
+ sender ( Address, required )
+ recipient ( Address, required )
+ createdAt: `2020-12-30T00:00:00.000Z` ( string, required )
+ returnLabelUrls ( array[ string ], optional )
+ error ( string, optional )

## ReturnLabelState (enum)
+ RequestingLabel
+ ResolvingLabel
+ Resolved
+ Error

## Address
+ companyName: Company XYZ ( string, optional )
+ name: John Dow ( string, required )
+ countryCode: AA ( string, required )
+ city: City ( string, required )
+ zipCode: 123456 ( string, required )
+ street: Street 123 ( string, required )
+ phone: 123456789 ( string, optional )
+ email: example@email.cmo ( string, optional )
